Subject: How To Be Civilized Online
Description: The internet allows us to express our opinions, good and bad, anonymously and instantaneously.  Learn how to be a better cyber-citizen.  Speakers include:Mitchell Bowling, John Belden - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Party Planning
Description: Whether it's a formal dinner or gaming night, how to prepare for, run, and still enjoy your get-together.  Speakers include:Wendy Carson, Mitchell Bowling, Hannah Davis - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Hakosot
Description: 'SAVE, YOUR, DIXIE CUPS, 'CAUSE WE'RE GONNA PLAY HAKOSOT! SAVE, YOUR, DIXIE CUPS, 'CAUSE WE'RE GONNA PLAY HAKOSOT!' Grab all your friends, and play this game of singing while passing cups.  Speakers include:Mitchell Bowling - Track: Gaming  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Is It Necessary to Unplug to Unwind?
Description: We have all heard the advice about taking time to remove ourselves from our digital devices, but is that really necessary?  Can one utilize technology to relax after a long day of using technology?  Speakers include:Mitchell Bowling - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes
